<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Event Registration Page</title>
    <style>
        /* Global Styling */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #eef2f3, #d9e4ec);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
        }

        /* Event Title and Description Styling */
        .event-header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .event-header h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .event-header h2 {
            color: #34495e;
        }

        .event-header h3 {
            color: #555;
        }

        .description {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ccc;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        /* Event Information Section */
        .event-details {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .event-details ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        /* Registration Form Card Layout */
        .registration-form {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        /* Fieldsets and Legends */
        fieldset {
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding: 15px;
        }

        legend {
            background: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        /* Input Elements styling */
        input[type="text"],
        input[type="email"],
        input[type="tel"],
        input[type="date"],
        select,
        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 8px;
            margin-top: 5px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            box-sizing: border-box; /* Proper alignment for 100% width */
        }

        input:focus,
        select:focus,
        textarea:focus {
            border-color: #3498db;
            outline: none;
        }

        .radio-group {
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        /* Declaration Section */
        .declaration {
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        /* Button Styling */
        .buttons {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        input[type="submit"],
        input[type="reset"] {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: none;
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin: 5px;
            transition: background 0.3s; /* Smooth visual feedback */
        }

        input[type="submit"] {
            background: #3498db;
        }

        input[type="reset"] {
            background: #e74c3c;
        }

        input[type="submit"]:hover {
            background: #2980b9;
        }

        input[type="reset"]:hover {
            background: #c0392b;
        }

        /* Participants Table Styling */
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        th {
            background: #3498db;
            color: white;
        }

        th, td {
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        tr:nth-child(even) {
            background: #f2f2f2;
        }

        tr:hover {
            background: #dfe6e9;
        }

        /* Footer Design */
        footer {
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <header class="event-header">
        <h1>SKP ARTS & SCIENCE COLLEGE</h1>
        <h2>WEB DEVELOPMENT AND AIML</h2>
        <h3>4 Days Event 2026</h3>
        <p class="description">
            [span_2](start_span)Intha Program moolama AI and WEB DEVELOPMENT thozhilnutpattin ethirkalam patri therinthu kollalam.[span_2](end_span)
        </p>
    </header>

    <section class="event-details">
        <h3>Event Details</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Date:</strong> 15th March 2026</li>
            <li><strong>Time:</strong> 10:00 AM to 4:00 PM</li>
            <li><strong>Venue:</strong> SKP Engineering Anna Auditorium</li>
            <li><strong>Organizer:</strong> HTGE, GUVI Technologies</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <form class="registration-form">
        <fieldset>
            <legend>Personal Information</legend>
            <label>Name</label>
            <input type="text">
            
            <label>Email</label>
            <input type="email">
            
            <label>Phone Number</label>
            <input type="tel">
            
            <label>Date of Birth</label>
            <input type="date">
            
            <label>Gender</label>
            <div class="radio-group">
                <input type="radio" name="gender" value="Male"> Male
                <input type="radio" name="gender" value="Female"> Female
            </div>
        </fieldset>

        <fieldset>
            <legend>Event Selection</legend>
            <label>Event</label>
            <select>
                <option>Workshop</option>
                <option>Seminar</option>
                <option>Presentation</option>
                <option>Hackathon</option>
                <option>Training</option>
                <option>Problem Solving</option>
            </select>
            
            <label>Mode of Participation</label>
            <div class="radio-group">
                <input type="radio" name="mode" value="Online"> Online
                <input type="radio" name="mode" value="Offline"> Offline
            </div>
        </fieldset>

        <fieldset>
            <legend>Additional Details</legend>
            <label>College / Company Name</label>
            <input type="text">
            
            <label>Upload ID Proof</label>
            <input type="file">
            
            <label>Comments / Expectations</label>
            <textarea rows="4"></textarea>
        </fieldset>

        <div class="declaration">
            <input type="checkbox"> I confirm that the above details are correct.
        </div>

        <div class="buttons">
            <input type="submit" value="Submit">
            <input type="reset" value="Reset">
        </div>
    </form>

    <section>
        <h3>Registered Participants</h3>
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Name</th>
                    <th>Email</th>
                    <th>Phone</th>
                    <th>Event</th>
                    <th>Mode</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>Tharun</td>
                    <td>Tharun143@mail.com</td>
                    <td>9976542095</td>
                    <td>Workshop</td>
                    <td>Offline</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </section>
</div>

<footer>
    <p>Contact Email: guvitech248@gmail.com | Help Desk: 1800-123-456</p>
    <p>&copy; 2026 HTGE, GUVI Technologies Innovative Solutions Pvt LTD. All Rights Reserved.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
                                        
